  "keyFeatures": [
    "Explainable credibility scoring across five levels (Credible to High-risk)",
    "Live web grounding via Tavily search and extract for time-sensitive claims",
    "Multi-model AI pipeline: Gemini primary with Azure AI Foundry / Llama 3.1 fallback",
    "Structured output: claims, flags, source notes, context notes, next steps, and citations",
    "Claim classification for time-sensitivity, breaking news, and high-stake events",
    "Heuristic policy-blocked fallback for robust analysis under all conditions",
    "Side-by-side comparison mode for two pieces of content",
    "Curated sample analyses for onboarding and demonstration"
  ],
